name: Kung Fu Beats: Fantasy Music Dojo
summary: In Kung Fu Beats, smash jade orbs in time with oriental tracks using your VR controllers. Each level—from bamboo forests to mountain dojos—offers new challenges and layouts. As the music speeds up, your speed, stamina, and timing are put to the test in a workout that feels like play. Track your high scores, climb the leaderboards, and unlock new stages, weapons, and bonus modes. Master the beat and crush every...
